  "course_description": "This course focuses on programming and data management, with an emphasis on building skills for economic analysis and data science. You will learn how to access and manipulate various types of datasets, including tabular data, text data, and social network data. You will learn essential computer literacy and concepts, and workflows for reproducible research.By the end of the course, you will have gained computing skills that can be applied to real-world big data scenarios. The course will use popular data analysis software such as R and Python, and leverage cloud computing for enhanced data processing capabilities. analysis software such as R and Python, and leverage cloud computing for enhanced data processing capabilities.",
